<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
    <div class="add-drama-width">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center">

                <div class="row g-lg-3 g-md-4 g-sm-4 mt-4 col-lg-3 add-drama-left-bar-margin">
                    <div class="add-drama-left-bar">
                        <div class="add-drama-left-bar-title">
                            <div>提供劇集資料注意事項</div>
                        </div>
                        <ol>
                            <li class="add-drama-left-bar-point">請確保劇集資料輸入無誤。</li>
                            <li class="add-drama-left-bar-point">任一劇集資料格式輸入錯誤將無法提交資料。</li>
                            <li class="add-drama-left-bar-point">如因任何輸入問題而無法提交劇集資料，歡迎隨時發送電郵致本網站作相關跟進。</li>
                            <li class="add-drama-left-bar-point">本網站在任何時候保留不新增 / 更改 / 刪除該劇集資料的權利。</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <form class="row g-3 col-lg-9 mt-4">
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-4 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaTitle" class="form-label">劇集名稱 (中文)</label>
                        <input id="addDramaTitle" class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="例子: 女神的教室" required>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <label for="addDramaTitleJp" class="form-label">劇集名稱 (日文)</label>
                        <input id="addDramaTitleJp" class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="例子: 女神の教室" required>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-4">
                        <label for="addDramaCategory" class="form-label">劇集類別</label>
                        <select id="addDramaCategory" class="form-select" aria-describedby="validationServer04Feedback" required>
                            <option selected disabled value="">請選擇</option>
                            <option>校園</option>
                            <option>政治</option>
                            <option>愛情</option>
                            <option>音樂</option>
                            <option>動漫改編</option>
                            <option>醫療</option>
                            <option>勵志</option>
                            <option>警察/刑事</option>
                            <option>小說/文學改編</option>
                            <option>喜劇</option>
                            <option>古裝</option>
                            <option>懸疑/推理</option>
                            <option>職場</option>
                            <option>家庭/族</option>
                            <option>錢關</option>
                            <option>料理/美食</option>
                            <option>恐怖</option>
                            <option>神秘</option>
                            <option>特攝</option>
                            <option>鐵路相關</option>
                            <option>真人改編</option>
                            <option>末日相關</option>
                            <option>其他</option>
                        </select>
                        <div id="validationServer04Feedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please select a valid state.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaIntroduction" class="form-label">劇集概要</label>
                        <textarea id="addDramaIntroduction" class="form-control" placeholder="建議輸入六十字以內。" required></textarea>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaTV" class="form-label">劇集播放電視台</label>
                        <select id="addDramaTV" class="form-select" aria-describedby="validationServer04Feedback" required>
                            <option selected disabled value="">請選擇</option>
                            <option>富士電視台</option>
                            <option>日本電視台</option>
                            <option>東京電視台</option>
                            <option>朝日電視台</option>
                            <option>TBS</option>
                            <option>NHK</option>
                            <option>Abema</option>
                            <option>Netflix</option>
                            <option>其他</option>
                        </select>
                        <div id="validationServer04Feedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please select a valid state.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <label for="addDramaDateOfBroadcast" class="form-label">劇集首播日期</label>
                        <input id="addDramaDateOfBroadcast" type="date" class="form-control input-date" required>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaWeek" class="form-label">劇集播放週</label>
                        <select id="addDramaWeek" class="form-select" aria-describedby="validationServer04Feedback" required>
                            <option selected disabled value="">請選擇</option>
                            <option>每週一</option>
                            <option>每週二</option>
                            <option>每週三</option>
                            <option>每週四</option>
                            <option>每週五</option>
                            <option>每週六</option>
                            <option>每週日</option>
                        </select>
                        <div id="validationServer04Feedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please select a valid state.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <label for="addDramaTimeOfBoardcast" class="form-label">劇集播放時間</label>
                        <input id="addDramaTimeOfBoardcast" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="例子: 21:00" required>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaActor" class="form-label">劇集主要演員</label>
                        <textarea id="addDramaActor" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="例子: 北川景子 / 柊木雫, 山田裕貴 / 藍井仁  (注意: 每套劇集最多只接受新增九名演員資料。)" required></textarea>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-6 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaRating" class="form-label">劇集收視率 (如有)</label>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input id="addDramaRating" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="例子: 10.5, 10, 9.1, 12 (按集數順序並以逗號分隔)">
                            <div class="input-group-text">%</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-lg-6">
                        <label for="addDramaMedia" class="form-label">劇集媒體資訊網址</label>
                        <input id="addDramaMedia" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="例子: https://www.youtube.com/embed/P90avWuEH_U" required>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaVideo" class="form-label">劇集來源網址 (如有) [僅限於磁力連結 Magnet URL]</label>
                        <textarea id="addDramaVideo" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="例子: magnet:?xt=urn:btih:2TP3A57GUMJ3KG4QWW3EE432WAL3575L, magnet:?xt=urn:btih:XGNKSKDBQVMFWWHLSTTNLJZ3GTDFJFKZ (按集數順序並以逗號分隔)" required></textarea>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-lg-12 mb-2">
                        <label for="addDramaCoverPhoto" class="form-label">上載劇集封面圖片</label>
                        <input id="addDramaCoverPhoto" type="file" class="form-control" accept=".jpg, .jpeg, .png" required>
                        <div class="valid-feedback">
                            Looks good!
                        </div>
                        <div id="validationServerUsernameFeedback" class="invalid-feedback">
                            Please choose a username.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <img id="addDramaCoverPhotoPreviewContainer" style="display:none;"></img>

                </form>

                <div class="col-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <button id="handleAddDramaBtn" class="btn" type="submit">提供劇集資料</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>